{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-staticfuse-gatsby-theme-publisher-src-templates-posts-single-js","path":"/blog/block-category-common/","result":{"pageContext":{"uri":"block-category-common","id":"cG9zdDoxNzc5","postId":1779,"title":"Block category: Common","content":"\n<p>The Common category includes the following blocks:<em> Paragraph, image, headings, list, gallery, quote, audio, cover, video.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The paragraph block is the default block type.&nbsp; It should not have any alignment of any kind. It should just flow like you would normally expect. Nothing fancy. Just straight up text, free flowing, with love.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This paragraph is left aligned.</p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>This italic paragraph is right aligned.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Neither of these paragraphs care about politics, but this one is bold, medium sized and has a drop cap.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">This paragraph is centered. </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">This paragraph prefers Jazz over Justin Timberlake. It also uses the small font size.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">This paragraph has something important to say:&nbsp; It has a large font size, which defaults to 36px.</p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:46px\">The huge text size defaults to 46px, but the size can be customized.</p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"background-color:#cf2e2e\" class=\"has-text-color has-background has-very-light-gray-color\">This paragraph is colorful, with a red background and white text.  Colored blocks should have a high enough contrast, so that the text is readable. </p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"color:#1e0566\" class=\"has-text-color\"><strong>Below this block, you will see a single image.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://wpthemetestdata.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/image-alignment-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 150x150\" class=\"wp-image-968\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h1>H1 Heading</h1>\n\n\n\n<h2>H2 Heading</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>H3 Heading</h3>\n\n\n\n<h4>H4 Heading</h4>\n\n\n\n<h5>H5 Heading</h5>\n\n\n\n<h6>H6 Heading</h6>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ordered list</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>The software should be licensed under the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GNU Public License</a>.</li><li>The software should be freely available to anyone to use for any purpose, and without permission.</li><li>The software should be open to modifications.<ol><li>Any modifications should be freely distributable at no cost and without permission from its creators.</li></ol></li><li>The software should provide a framework for translation to make it globally accessible to speakers of all languages.</li><li>The software should provide a framework for extensions so modifications and enhancements can be made without modifying core code</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>Unordered list</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>One</li><li>Two</li><li>Three<ul><li>Four</li></ul></li><li>Five</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0747.jpg\" alt=\"Brazil Beach\" data-id=\"769\" \ndata-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/img_0747/\" class=\"wp-image-769\" srcset=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0747.jpg 1600w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0747-300x200.jpg 300w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0747-768x512.jpg 768w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0747-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0747-1568x1045.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" />\n<figcaption>Jericoacoara Ceara Brasil</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0513-1.jpg\" alt=\"Huatulco Coastline\" data-id=\"768\" \ndata-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/alas-i-have-found-my-shangri-la/\" class=\"wp-image-768\" srcset=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0513-1.jpg 800w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0513-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/img_0513-1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" />\n<figcaption>Sunrise over the coast in Huatulco, Oaxaca, Mexico</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\">\n<figure><img src=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/windmill.jpg\" alt=\"Windmill\" data-id=\"767\" \ndata-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery//dcf-1-0/\" class=\"wp-image-767\" srcset=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/windmill.jpg 1600w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/windmill-300x225.jpg 300w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/windmill-768x576.jpg 768w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/windmill-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/windmill-1568x1176.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" />\n<figcaption>Windmill shrouded in fog at a farm outside of Walker, Iowa</figcaption></figure></li>\n<li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://wpthemetestdata.files.wordpress.com/2008/06/img_8399.jpg\" \nalt=\"Boat Barco Texture\" data-id=\"771\" data-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/img_8399/\" \nclass=\"wp-image-771\"/><figcaption>Boat BW PB Barco Texture Beautiful Fishing</figcaption></figure></li>\n<li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"h