316-1568x1176.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" />\n<figcaption>Sea and rocks, Plimmerton, New Zealand</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure>\n<img src=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/michelle_049.jpg\" alt=\"Big Sur\" data-id=\"766\" \ndata-link=\"https://wpthemetestdata.wordpress.com/2010/09/10/post-format-gallery/michelle_049/\" class=\"wp-image-766\" srcset=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/michelle_049.jpg 1600w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/michelle_049-300x225.jpg 300w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/michelle_049-768x576.jpg 768w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/michelle_049-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/michelle_049-1568x1176.jpg 1568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" />\n<figcaption>Beach at Big Sur, CA</figcaption></figure></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Quote</p><cite>Cite</cite></blockquote>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-audio\"><audio controls src=\"https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/originaldixielandjazzbandwithalbernard-stlouisblues.mp3\"></audio></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim\" style=\"background-image:url(https://publishertheme.staticfuse.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/dsc04563.jpg)\"><p class=\"wp-block-cover-text\">Cover block with background image</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>The file block has a setting that lets us show or hide a download button with editable text: </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a href=\"https://wpthemetestdata.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/file_block.pdf\">File Block PDF</a><a href=\"https://wpthemetestdata.files.wordpress.com/2018/11/file_block.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download>Download</a></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a hre